      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<h1>Faction Sigils &amp; Wax</h1><p>Seven drop-in sigil handouts you can show at the table when a faction enters the scene. The pages below are page-per-sigil for easy showcase mode in Foundry; the images themselves live at <code>modules/blooming-rot-2/assets/sigils/</code>.</p><ul><li><strong>Brass Crow</strong> &mdash; the brass figure above the lintel of the Foreign Quarter counting-house in Greyhawk City. Show when the party first reaches Tinker's Way.</li><li><strong>Kestrel &amp; Reed, Foreign Letters</strong> &mdash; pressed silver-and-pewter on dark teal. Show on K&amp;R packets or receipts.</li><li><strong>Cindren &amp; Vhal</strong> &mdash; interlocking iron carriage-wheels on wine-red. Show on any firm correspondence in Phases 2&ndash;4.</li><li><strong>Hand of the Duke (intact)</strong> &mdash; brass quill crossed by a silver oath-bar. Caelith's pin in Phases 1&ndash;4.</li><li><strong>Hand of the Duke (broken)</strong> &mdash; the same device, oath-bar snapped. Caelith's pin <em>after</em> Closure passes in Phase 5.</li><li><strong>Yeomanry Wheatsheaf</strong> &mdash; bronze sheaf on dark green; Loftwick councilor insignia.</li><li><strong>Unknown Wax Recipe-Family</strong> &mdash; dark purple-brown wax seal, seven vertical lines under a low arch. The thing Aldea cannot place. <em>Show only when the party recovers a marked packet.</em></li></ul>"
      }
    },
